  "detailed_description": "When you wake up, you find yourself trapped in a mysterious laboratory...<br><br>This laboratory is filled with unknown dangers. You must utilize the capabilities of the Telemorpher to overcome obstacles and uncover the truth behind the laboratory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041070/extras/2bd12a0727621c154da3bc9a2b57bf1b.poster.avif?t=1744955826\" width=762 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041070/extras/2bd12a0727621c154da3bc9a2b57bf1b.webm?t=1744955826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041070/extras/2bd12a0727621c154da3bc9a2b57bf1b.mp4?t=1744955826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each level presents its unique challenges and hidden secrets, waiting for you to discover and unlock.<br><br>In addition to using the Telemorpher for teleportation, you can also utilize various objects and mechanisms in the surrounding environment to help you reach your goals. But beware, the laboratory may harbor unforeseen dangers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041070/extras/35ea76e109a6479df1fb611847a06902.poster.avif?t=1744955826\" width=762 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041070/extras/35ea76e109a6479df1fb611847a06902.webm?t=1744955826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041070/extras/35ea76e109a6479df1fb611847a06902.mp4?t=1744955826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
